<H3> <TI>   Italy `Not Satisfied' With EU Milk Quota </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italy `Not Satisfied' With EU Milk Quota </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2206110394 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1838 GMT 21 
Jun 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR2206110394 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
