<H4>    Approves Government Program </H4>

<F P=102> LD2206145194 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 1342 GMT 22 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2206145194 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin DDP/ADN </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Halle/Saale (DDP/ADN) -- The SPD will go into the 
Bundestag election campaign with a government program for more 
jobs, social justice, and an environmentally friendly 
modernization of the economy and society. The delegates to the 
election party congress in Halle approved a draft program to 
this effect this afternoon with no votes against. A few 
delegates abstained. 

</TEXT>

