<H3> <TI>   Social Affairs Minister Sigurdardottir Resigns 22 Jun </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Social Affairs Minister Sigurdardottir Resigns 22 Jun </PHRASE></F></HT>

