<H3> <TI>   Kohl `Very Happy' With Results </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kohl `Very Happy' With Results </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2706120394 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 1141 GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>
