<H3> <TI>   CSU Chairman Criticizes Postcommunist PDS </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    CSU Chairman Criticizes Postcommunist PDS </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2606124494 Berlin DDP/ADN in German 1136 GMT 26 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2606124494 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin DDP/ADN </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Nuremberg (DDP/ADN) -- Theo Waigel, chairman of the 
CSU [Christian Social Union], has again sharply attacked the 
SED's [Socialist Unity Party] successor party, the PDS [Party of 
Democratic Socialists]. Waigel told the regional conference of 
the Bavarian Young Union [CSU's youth organization] here today 
that the "criminal SED/PDS" ought to be "turfed out of the 
