then we should not tolerate any former communists or 
neocommunists," the head of the CSU said. He is not, he said, 
fighting against the Republicans' leader Franz Schoenhuber so 
that "a Mr. Gysi [leader of PDS] can travel from talk show to 
talk show." 
  Just as the CDU [Christian Democratic Union]/CSU ruled out 
any cooperation with the far-right Republicans, so it should 
distance itself from the PDS as well, Waigel said. 

